            "title": "港股開升190點 長和挫逾6%友邦跌逾2%  科網股升",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股恒生指數開升190點或0.81%，報23653點，恒生國企指數升96點或1.12%，報8737點，恒生科技指數升78點或1.36%，報6826點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/03/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股4.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">大市成交31.19億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">友邦(01299)開跌2.07%，報61.5元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長和(00001)挫6.28%，報46.3元，港澳辦轉載評論文章，質疑長和出售港口資產交易並非普通商業行為。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)升2.28%，報134.5元; 騰訊(00700)升1.08%，報513元。美團(03690)升2.37%，報168.4元</p>\n</div>",
